betterquesting:10.desc:8:
There are many different tiers of many types of lootbags that you will recieve from this questbook. The lootbags can be incredibly useful for giving yourself a little resource boost, or even an early technology boost.

There are two paths you can take when it comes to upgrading your lootbags, you can either enchant it with fortune, or you can upgrade the bag itself. Enchanting the lootbag with fortune will increase the chances of more rare drops being given to you on opening, while upgrading the bag itself will change the item pool to that of the upgraded bag. 

If you're looking to maximize your advantage it's recommended you both uptier your lootbag AND apply the fortune upgrade. 

[note]Be sure to use NEI to see all of this information. Use 'U' on your lootbag and you will be able to see the potential drops, the drop chances based on fortune levels, and you will be able to see recipes for uptiering the bag.[/note]
